BUTTS
v.
CUYAHOGA CTY. 2019-0129 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 8, 2019

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

On respondents' motions to dismiss. Motions granted. Cause dismissed. O'CONNOR, C.J., and KENNEDY, FRENCH, FISCHER, DEWINE, and DONNELLY, JJ., concur. STEWART, J., not participating.
